-- 2010-10-16T01:50:41Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-16/china-environment-risk-insurance-pilot-plan-starts-in-8-cities-circ-says.html
A Chinese environment risk insurance
pilot program has started in eight cities, Zhou Yanli, vice
chairman of the China Insurance Regulatory Commission, said at a
financial conference in Shanghai.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
